race.comment: GOLD CAPITAL (5) ran a good race last start to finish second over 1500m at Muswellbrook. May appreciate coming back in journey. Strong run last time and shapes as a major threat. SUGAR ISLAND (3) finished tenth over 1400m at Sunshine Coast at his most recent appearance on August 17. Comes here with definite claims. SET TO PROPHET (2) ran a very close third last start over 1600m at Tamworth to make it four minor placings in a row. Can measure up again. NEED A MIRACLE (1) missed the placings two runs back then didn't do any better last start when 3 lengths away in fifth over 1600m at Scone. Finds a nice race and can atone.
